# Always follow

- Respect layer boundaries:
  - `src/pages/` orchestrates + renders UI.
  - `src/components/` reusable UI.
  - `src/api/` all external IO (AI/Supabase/HTTP).
  - `src/lib/` pure logic/utilities (and prompt templates when possible).
- AI changes:
  - Keep safety/disclaimer behavior consistent (no legal advice).
  - Prefer moving system/persona prompt constants into `src/lib/ai/*`.
- Error handling:
  - `src/api/*` throw clear errors.
  - UI catches and shows user-friendly messages.
- Testing:
  - Pure logic => Vitest unit tests in `src/__tests__/`.
  - Before PR: `npm run lint` and `npm run test` must pass.

